configure your jobs to send log information to Amazon S3.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 EncryptionKeyArn => Str

The KMS key ARN to encrypt the logs published to the given Amazon S3
destination.


=head2 LogUri => Str

The Amazon S3 destination URI for log publishing.



